WEBVTT

1
00:00:15.336 --> 00:00:18.961
You refer to the prophecy of the
one who will bring balance to the Force.

2
00:00:20.461 --> 00:00:22.211
You believe it's this boy?

3
00:00:26.420 --> 00:00:29.670
Anakin Skywalker. meet Obi-Wan Kenobi.

4
00:00:31.461 --> 00:00:34.295
<i>Clouded this boy's future is.</i>

5
00:00:36.045 --> 00:00:39.420
The boy is dangerous.
They all sense it. Why can't you?

6
00:00:40.045 --> 00:00:42.628
An apprentice you have. Qui-Gon.

7
00:00:42.711 --> 00:00:44.920
Impossible to take on a second.

8
00:00:45.003 --> 00:00:47.461
- Obi-Wan is ready.
- I am ready to face the trials.

9
00:00:53.295 --> 00:00:55.045
<i>You've been a good apprentice.
Obi-Wan.</i>

10
00:00:57.503 --> 00:00:59.211
No!

11
00:01:00.211 --> 00:01:02.336
<i>I foresee you will become
a great Jedi Knight.</i>

12
00:01:02.420 --> 00:01:03.878
Obi-Wan.

13
00:01:03.961 --> 00:01:05.961
Promise me you will train the boy.

14
00:01:06.545 --> 00:01:07.545
Yes. Master.

15
00:01:07.628 --> 00:01:11.045
He will bring balance.

16
00:01:11.461 --> 00:01:14.586
Master Yoda. I gave Qui-Gon my word.

17
00:01:15.253 --> 00:01:18.045
<i>Your apprentice Skywalker will be.</i>

18
00:01:22.586 --> 00:01:23.586
What took you so long?

19
00:01:26.628 --> 00:01:28.295
<i>Obi-Wan is a great mentor.</i>

20
00:01:29.253 --> 00:01:30.545
<i>As wise as Master Yoda</i>

21
00:01:32.003 --> 00:01:33.920
<i>and as powerful as Master Windu.</i>

22
00:01:34.545 --> 00:01:36.836
You are the most gifted Jedi
I have ever met.

23
00:01:38.503 --> 00:01:41.378
<i>I see you becoming
the greatest of all the Jedi.</i>

24
00:01:42.711 --> 00:01:43.753
<i>I feel lost.</i>

25
00:01:44.878 --> 00:01:47.753
Lost? What do you mean?

26
00:01:47.836 --> 00:01:50.461
<i>I'm not the Jedi I should be.
I want more.</i>

27
00:01:51.128 --> 00:01:52.128
And I know I shouldn't.

28
00:01:53.086 --> 00:01:54.836
<i>How do you know the ways of the Force?</i>

29
00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:58.586
My mentor taught me everything
about the Force.

30
00:01:59.628 --> 00:02:02.336
Even the nature of the dark side

31
00:02:03.961 --> 00:02:05.545
Only through me

32
00:02:05.628 --> 00:02:09.253
can you achieve a power
greater than any Jedi.

33
00:02:09.461 --> 00:02:11.170
I can't.

34
00:02:11.628 --> 00:02:12.753
Don't give up. Padmé.

35
00:02:14.211 --> 00:02:16.378
<i>The power to save Padmé.</i>

36
00:02:17.128 --> 00:02:19.211
I found a way to save you.

37
00:02:19.295 --> 00:02:24.295
<i>Twisted by the dark side
young Skywalker has become.</i>

38
00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:28.753
The boy you trained. gone he is.

39
00:02:28.836 --> 00:02:30.295
I will not kill Anakin.

40
00:02:32.836 --> 00:02:35.003
This is the end for you. my master.

41
00:02:35.628 --> 00:02:37.003
I have failed you. Anakin.

42
00:02:37.961 --> 00:02:38.961
I have failed you.

43
00:02:40.753 --> 00:02:43.753
It's over. Anakin. I have the high ground.

44
00:02:43.836 --> 00:02:46.503
You underestimate my power.

45
00:02:49.503 --> 00:02:51.253
You were the Chosen One!

46
00:02:51.336 --> 00:02:54.211
It was said that you would
destroy the Sith. not join them!

47
00:02:57.170 --> 00:02:58.711
He's still alive.

48
00:03:04.086 --> 00:03:05.878
<i>You were my brother. Anakin.</i>

49
00:03:08.211 --> 00:03:13.003
<i>You shall be known
as Darth Vader.</i>

50
00:03:14.211 --> 00:03:15.295
Obi-Wan?

51
00:03:16.086 --> 00:03:17.878
There's good in him.

52
00:03:20.003 --> 00:03:21.086
<i>Rise.</i>

53
00:03:23.961 --> 00:03:27.545
<i>Hidden.
safe the children must be kept.</i>

54
00:03:30.295 --> 00:03:31.628
<i>We must take them somewhere</i>

55
00:03:31.711 --> 00:03:33.753
<i>where the Sith
will not sense their presence.</i>

56
00:03:35.086 --> 00:03:36.836
My wife and I will take the girl.

57
00:03:37.545 --> 00:03:39.961
<i>We've always talked
of adopting a baby girl.</i>

58
00:03:40.753 --> 00:03:41.753
<i>Leia.</i>

59
00:03:41.836 --> 00:03:42.836
And what of the boy?

60
00:03:43.253 --> 00:03:44.253
<i>Luke.</i>

61
00:03:44.420 --> 00:03:47.045
To Tatooine. To his family send him.

62
00:03:47.128 --> 00:03:49.086
I will take the child and watch over him.

63
00:03:51.128 --> 00:03:52.378
<i>In your solitude...</i>

64
00:03:53.086 --> 00:03:54.920
<i>training I have for you.</i>

65
00:03:55.003 --> 00:03:56.961
<i>Your old master.</i>

66
00:03:57.503 --> 00:04:00.586
<i>How to commune with him I will teach you.</i>

67
00:04:57.420 --> 00:04:58.920
This way! Quick!

68
00:05:04.128 --> 00:05:05.128
Come on! Let's go!

69
00:05:05.211 --> 00:05:07.461
- Let's go!
- This way!

70
00:05:10.128 --> 00:05:11.128
Come on! Let's go!

71
00:05:11.211 --> 00:05:13.545
- This way.
- Hurry!

72
00:05:15.253 --> 00:05:16.711
Watch out!

73
00:05:20.045 --> 00:05:21.795
Come on! Move! Quick!

74
00:05:26.336 --> 00:05:29.045
- Go. Come on! Go. Go! Go!
- Run! This way! Hurry!

75
00:05:39.253 --> 00:05:40.420
No!

76
00:05:44.795 --> 00:05:45.795
What do we do now?

77
00:05:46.670 --> 00:05:47.670
We run.

78
00:05:50.920 --> 00:05:53.920
<i>Execute Order 66.</i>

79
00:05:54.795 --> 00:05:57.961
<i>Execute Order 66.</i>

80
00:05:59.003 --> 00:06:02.420
<i>Execute Order 66.</i>

81
00:08:34.628 --> 00:08:37.295
You know who we are.

82
00:08:37.961 --> 00:08:38.961
Inquisitors.

83
00:08:39.045 --> 00:08:41.003
You know what we do?

84
00:08:41.086 --> 00:08:42.336
You hunt Jedi.

85
00:08:42.420 --> 00:08:47.586
In actuality. I would say
the Jedi hunt themselves.

86
00:08:52.586 --> 00:08:56.503
Do you know the key
to hunting a Jedi. friend?

87
00:08:57.795 --> 00:08:59.628
It is patience.

88
00:09:02.628 --> 00:09:05.128
Jedi cannot help what they are.

89
00:09:06.753 --> 00:09:09.336
Their compassion leaves a trail.

90
00:09:10.211 --> 00:09:16.295
For example.
in our line of work. rumors run rampant.

91
00:09:17.045 --> 00:09:19.045
Here's one I heard just recently.

92
00:09:19.128 --> 00:09:24.461
It involves a Jedi hiding right here
in your lovely saloon.

93
00:09:26.253 --> 00:09:29.211
Let's say ours is a wanderer.

94
00:09:30.503 --> 00:09:32.711
Maybe he's looking for people like him.

95
00:09:33.878 --> 00:09:36.628
Comes across this establishment.

96
00:09:36.711 --> 00:09:37.795
Nice place.

97
00:09:39.295 --> 00:09:42.878
And then he sees you.

98
00:09:44.795 --> 00:09:45.961
A man in need.

99
00:09:48.545 --> 00:09:50.795
Perhaps the locals are stealing from you.

100
00:09:52.211 --> 00:09:53.503
Threatening you.

101
00:09:54.086 --> 00:09:56.836
So what is the Jedi to do?

102
00:09:59.753 --> 00:10:03.211
Help you and risk exposure?

103
00:10:05.295 --> 00:10:06.378
Or move on?

104
00:10:07.586 --> 00:10:12.878
Now. if he were smart. he'd keep moving.
but the Jedi Code is like an itch.

105
00:10:12.961 --> 00:10:14.795
He cannot help it.

106
00:10:14.878 --> 00:10:18.253
So he steps in and saves your saloon.

107
00:10:18.336 --> 00:10:20.878
You offer him a place to hide.

108
00:10:20.961 --> 00:10:23.336
Fresh water. shade from the suns.

109
00:10:23.420 --> 00:10:27.586
but the stories. they begin
and they travel quickly.

110
00:10:27.670 --> 00:10:30.711
His compassion has been his undoing.

111
00:10:37.420 --> 00:10:38.503
There.

112
00:10:45.961 --> 00:10:47.461
Prepare him for interrogation.

113
00:10:47.545 --> 00:10:50.003
You're wasting your time.
You know that. right?

114
00:10:50.878 --> 00:10:52.003
You'll never find us all.

115
00:11:06.545 --> 00:11:08.211
You are reckless.

116
00:11:09.503 --> 00:11:10.670
Why chase after scraps?

117
00:11:10.753 --> 00:11:13.086
Scraps are all we have left.

118
00:11:13.170 --> 00:11:14.795
Then we should be hunting bigger prey.

119
00:11:14.878 --> 00:11:18.003
He is not yours to find.
We are past this. Third Sister.

120
00:11:18.086 --> 00:11:19.961
I will not warn you again.

121
00:11:20.045 --> 00:11:24.503
You will forget this fixation with Kenobi.
or I will relieve you of your duties.

122
00:11:24.586 --> 00:11:25.670
Is that clear?

123
00:11:27.920 --> 00:11:30.128
Yes. Grand Inquisitor.

124
00:11:35.961 --> 00:11:37.586
Consider him forgotten.

125
00:13:14.878 --> 00:13:16.128
It's only half.

126
00:13:19.003 --> 00:13:20.003
Please. I have a family.

127
00:13:22.170 --> 00:13:23.878
One more word. I take it all.

128
00:13:26.545 --> 00:13:27.545
Keep moving.

129
00:13:34.170 --> 00:13:35.503
Something you want to say?

130
00:16:17.920 --> 00:16:19.253
You're late.

131
00:16:21.295 --> 00:16:22.461
Do you have it?

132
00:16:31.961 --> 00:16:33.378
I'll give you...

133
00:16:34.295 --> 00:16:35.503
I'll give you 50.

134
00:16:44.045 --> 00:16:46.878
Yes. I had some parts stolen.
I need a new processor board.

135
00:16:53.170 --> 00:16:56.503
Teeka. if you're gonna steal my parts
and then sell them back to me.

136
00:16:56.586 --> 00:16:59.461
could you at least clean them first
as a courtesy?

137
00:17:23.420 --> 00:17:24.420
A Jedi?

138
00:17:33.920 --> 00:17:35.586
Well. don't count on it.

139
00:17:36.586 --> 00:17:38.961
I've heard the Jedi are all but extinct.

140
00:17:41.128 --> 00:17:42.211
Here.

141
00:17:47.586 --> 00:17:49.211
Well. thank you. Teeka. Goodbye.

142
00:18:04.086 --> 00:18:05.420
<i>I know there's…</i>

143
00:18:08.253 --> 00:18:09.628
<i>You were my brother. Anakin!</i>

144
00:18:12.586 --> 00:18:14.628
Promise me you will train the boy.

145
00:18:16.170 --> 00:18:17.211
<i>Obi-Wan...</i>

146
00:18:17.961 --> 00:18:20.378
<i>Only pain will you find.</i>

147
00:18:21.086 --> 00:18:23.253
<i>There's good in him.
I know there's...</i>

148
00:18:24.128 --> 00:18:25.420
<i>You were the Chosen One!</i>

149
00:18:27.503 --> 00:18:28.670
I hate you!

150
00:18:50.461 --> 00:18:51.545
Master Qui-Gon.

151
00:18:55.753 --> 00:18:56.836
Master?

152
00:19:49.878 --> 00:19:52.545
Grab two of those canisters.

153
00:20:05.753 --> 00:20:06.836
Luke?

154
00:20:11.795 --> 00:20:12.878
Luke!

155
00:20:13.711 --> 00:20:14.711
Luke!

156
00:20:14.795 --> 00:20:16.628
Did he go back inside?

157
00:20:16.711 --> 00:20:17.795
He's run off.

158
00:20:19.836 --> 00:20:20.920
Luke?

159
00:20:26.753 --> 00:20:27.836
Luke?

160
00:20:32.795 --> 00:20:33.878
Luke?

161
00:21:43.211 --> 00:21:44.295
Master.

162
00:21:45.711 --> 00:21:47.961
I thought I saw you in the town.
but I wasn't sure.

163
00:21:48.045 --> 00:21:49.586
I didn't think you'd survived.

164
00:21:49.670 --> 00:21:51.670
You're making some kind of mistake.

165
00:21:51.753 --> 00:21:53.295
I'm sorry. my name is Nari.

166
00:21:54.211 --> 00:21:55.253
Um. there's no mistake.

167
00:21:56.878 --> 00:21:58.586
You're looking for somebody else.

168
00:21:59.836 --> 00:22:01.253
What are you doing here. Obi-Wan?

169
00:22:01.336 --> 00:22:02.461
My name is Ben.

170
00:22:03.295 --> 00:22:04.378
Come on. please.

171
00:22:04.878 --> 00:22:05.961
Please.

172
00:22:07.545 --> 00:22:09.378
You have no idea what I've been through.

173
00:22:23.045 --> 00:22:24.211
You must leave.

174
00:22:25.128 --> 00:22:26.420
You'll draw too much attention.

175
00:22:26.503 --> 00:22:27.795
But I have nowhere to go.

176
00:22:27.878 --> 00:22:30.253
They're hunting me. You have to help me.

177
00:22:31.795 --> 00:22:32.878
You want my help?

178
00:22:33.336 --> 00:22:34.420
Take this.

179
00:22:34.920 --> 00:22:37.753
Walk into the middle of the desert
and bury it in the ground.

180
00:22:40.461 --> 00:22:41.461
Stay hidden.

181
00:22:43.253 --> 00:22:44.253
Live a normal life.

182
00:22:44.336 --> 00:22:47.170
What about the people that need us?
What about the fight?

183
00:22:48.503 --> 00:22:49.670
The fight is done.

184
00:22:50.545 --> 00:22:51.628
We lost.

185
00:22:54.086 --> 00:22:55.170
What happened to you?

186
00:22:57.211 --> 00:22:58.711
You were once a great Jedi.

187
00:23:01.795 --> 00:23:03.878
The time of the Jedi is over.

188
00:23:09.336 --> 00:23:10.628
Go back to the town.

189
00:23:11.836 --> 00:23:12.920
Let it go.

190
00:23:58.253 --> 00:23:59.711
We're going to be late.

191
00:23:59.795 --> 00:24:01.670
Come on. let's hurry it along.

192
00:24:01.753 --> 00:24:02.753
How is she doing?

193
00:24:02.836 --> 00:24:03.836
She's ready?

194
00:24:04.420 --> 00:24:05.503
Great.

195
00:24:06.128 --> 00:24:07.378
Thank you.

196
00:24:07.461 --> 00:24:09.920
Remember.
my sister's whole family is coming.

197
00:24:10.420 --> 00:24:11.711
We need their support.

198
00:24:11.795 --> 00:24:13.378
So try not to make anyone cry.

199
00:24:13.461 --> 00:24:15.920
There will be sweetmallows
at the reception after.

200
00:24:16.628 --> 00:24:19.045
If you behave. I will let you...

201
00:24:24.920 --> 00:24:27.711
She insisted
you would find it amusing. Your Highness.

202
00:24:32.795 --> 00:24:35.045
She's either in the cellar.
in the kitchen...

203
00:24:35.878 --> 00:24:37.586
...or in the woods.

204
00:25:18.586 --> 00:25:20.003
Medical freighter.

205
00:25:21.503 --> 00:25:23.378
Pleasure barge. boring.

206
00:25:25.128 --> 00:25:27.128
Casino ship? Not bad.

207
00:25:29.461 --> 00:25:31.461
Ooh. A Tri-wing. That's a new one.

208
00:25:32.836 --> 00:25:34.670
Ooh. An Aquillian Ranger.

209
00:25:34.753 --> 00:25:38.128
Probably scouting for Merson pirates.

210
00:25:39.795 --> 00:25:41.795
No? Trader. maybe?

211
00:25:41.878 --> 00:25:43.045
Leia Organa!

212
00:25:44.920 --> 00:25:46.670
You had to do this today?

213
00:25:46.753 --> 00:25:47.753
Do what?

214
00:25:47.836 --> 00:25:48.920
Down.

215
00:25:53.920 --> 00:25:55.836
It is like raising a Glor-ag.

216
00:26:01.753 --> 00:26:03.086
No Lola for the rest of the day.

217
00:26:03.170 --> 00:26:05.211
But she didn't do anything.

218
00:26:05.295 --> 00:26:06.295
Shut her down.

219
00:26:07.836 --> 00:26:08.920
I mean it.

220
00:26:15.545 --> 00:26:18.503
If you behaved as well as you climb.

221
00:26:19.045 --> 00:26:20.670
you'd be a senator already.

222
00:26:22.711 --> 00:26:25.170
You'll have to change
in the speeder. Come.

223
00:26:25.253 --> 00:26:28.670
It's not like anyone would miss me
if I wasn't there.

224
00:26:28.753 --> 00:26:29.836
I'd miss you.

225
00:26:29.920 --> 00:26:31.670
All I ever do is wave.

226
00:26:31.753 --> 00:26:33.336
Then do more than wave.

227
00:26:33.420 --> 00:26:35.545
You get out of this what you put into it.

228
00:26:37.295 --> 00:26:38.461
I'm sorry. Mother.

229
00:26:39.128 --> 00:26:40.461
I really am.

230
00:26:41.045 --> 00:26:43.336
I promise I won't do it again.

231
00:26:49.253 --> 00:26:52.003
You know. I can feel you doing that.

232
00:26:52.711 --> 00:26:53.711
Come on.

233
00:26:53.795 --> 00:26:55.711
It's like living in a prison.

234
00:26:55.795 --> 00:26:56.878
A prison?

235
00:27:55.336 --> 00:27:57.003
I want you to stay away from him.

236
00:27:58.295 --> 00:28:00.086
We don't need anything from you. Ben.

237
00:28:00.170 --> 00:28:01.753
It's just a toy.

238
00:28:01.836 --> 00:28:03.378
It's a lot more than that.

239
00:28:03.461 --> 00:28:06.253
There's more to life than your farm. Owen.

240
00:28:06.336 --> 00:28:09.253
He needs to see that.
There's a whole galaxy out there.

241
00:28:09.336 --> 00:28:12.628
I'm asking you to leave us alone. Ben.

242
00:28:12.711 --> 00:28:13.711
I mean it.

243
00:28:14.211 --> 00:28:15.211
Is he okay?

244
00:28:16.545 --> 00:28:18.420
You don't care if he's okay.

245
00:28:19.711 --> 00:28:21.045
You care if he's showing.

246
00:28:21.128 --> 00:28:22.836
He's my responsibility. Owen.

247
00:28:22.920 --> 00:28:24.586
- I'm his uncle.
- We talked about this.

248
00:28:24.670 --> 00:28:27.086
When the time comes. he must be trained.

249
00:28:27.170 --> 00:28:28.545
Like you trained his father?

250
00:28:30.128 --> 00:28:32.211
Anakin is dead. Ben.

251
00:28:33.795 --> 00:28:36.211
and I won't let you
make the same mistake twice.

252
00:28:37.545 --> 00:28:41.211
So. leave him on the farm with his family.
where he belongs.

253
00:28:43.836 --> 00:28:45.836
Move. Now.

254
00:28:46.295 --> 00:28:48.211
Get back.

255
00:28:49.378 --> 00:28:50.461
All of you.

256
00:28:52.003 --> 00:28:53.086
Out of the way.

257
00:28:56.670 --> 00:28:57.836
Back up.

258
00:29:03.503 --> 00:29:05.336
You know why we are here.

259
00:29:07.170 --> 00:29:11.336
There is a Jedi hiding on this planet.

260
00:29:11.420 --> 00:29:13.961
We need to know where he is.

261
00:29:15.336 --> 00:29:16.795
You will be rewarded well.

262
00:29:16.878 --> 00:29:17.920
Or you'll be punished!

263
00:29:18.003 --> 00:29:19.045
Reva!

264
00:29:19.128 --> 00:29:20.670
Hands go first!

265
00:29:22.961 --> 00:29:25.628
That way. when you reach for anything.

266
00:29:28.253 --> 00:29:29.336
you think of us.

267
00:29:34.836 --> 00:29:36.420
This is the Outer Rim.

268
00:29:37.670 --> 00:29:39.253
You have no rights here.

269
00:29:39.795 --> 00:29:41.586
We're not under the Empire's...

270
00:29:44.420 --> 00:29:46.461
All we want is information.

271
00:29:47.211 --> 00:29:52.961
If anyone knows anything about a Jedi...

272
00:29:58.420 --> 00:29:59.586
You know something?

273
00:30:07.420 --> 00:30:08.503
What's your name?

274
00:30:09.753 --> 00:30:10.878
Owen.

275
00:30:11.836 --> 00:30:12.920
Owen.

276
00:30:13.336 --> 00:30:14.670
Farmer. right?

277
00:30:16.086 --> 00:30:17.086
Wife?

278
00:30:17.170 --> 00:30:18.170
Kids?

279
00:30:19.586 --> 00:30:21.003
My family's of no concern to you.

280
00:30:21.086 --> 00:30:22.378
They might be.

281
00:30:22.461 --> 00:30:25.086
- You got a Jedi on that farm. too?
- No.

282
00:30:25.170 --> 00:30:26.420
Why should I believe you?

283
00:30:26.503 --> 00:30:28.295
I have no love for the Jedi.

284
00:30:29.420 --> 00:30:30.503
Jedi are vermin.

285
00:30:31.670 --> 00:30:33.378
I kill vermin on my farm.

286
00:30:34.378 --> 00:30:35.878
You protect your family.

287
00:30:38.586 --> 00:30:39.836
I like that. Owen.

288
00:30:42.670 --> 00:30:43.670
It's important.

289
00:30:50.961 --> 00:30:53.045
You think you could protect them from me?

290
00:30:57.003 --> 00:31:02.420
Tell me where the Jedi is.
or this man and his family die!

291
00:31:05.420 --> 00:31:06.920
The Jedi are cowards.

292
00:31:09.003 --> 00:31:10.836
They failed you.

293
00:31:10.920 --> 00:31:13.670
abandoned you.

294
00:31:14.295 --> 00:31:16.961
There is no point in protecting them.

295
00:31:17.045 --> 00:31:19.086
They would not do the same for you.

296
00:31:23.670 --> 00:31:25.211
But you can save this man.

297
00:31:31.711 --> 00:31:33.336
Save his family.

298
00:31:39.628 --> 00:31:40.753
Enough!

299
00:31:42.503 --> 00:31:44.336
If you remember anything.

300
00:31:44.878 --> 00:31:46.461
rewards will be given.

301
00:31:48.961 --> 00:31:50.961
Stand down. Third Sister.

302
00:31:53.211 --> 00:31:54.295
Now!

303
00:31:56.753 --> 00:31:58.170
Next time. Owen.

304
00:32:04.586 --> 00:32:06.170
Ah! Move.

305
00:32:15.253 --> 00:32:18.211
You are too impulsive.

306
00:32:18.795 --> 00:32:20.295
I'm sick of wasting time!

307
00:32:21.045 --> 00:32:22.711
This place is beneath us!

308
00:32:23.295 --> 00:32:25.045
The Grand Inquisitor was right.

309
00:32:26.586 --> 00:32:28.128
You still want Kenobi.

310
00:32:30.003 --> 00:32:33.128
But he's gone. and you won't find him.

311
00:32:33.920 --> 00:32:36.503
We spent the last ten years
looking for him.

312
00:32:38.170 --> 00:32:40.503
Maybe you've been looking
in the wrong places.

313
00:32:41.378 --> 00:32:44.795
What is it you think you will gain
by capturing him?

314
00:32:46.170 --> 00:32:47.378
What I'm owed.

315
00:32:52.711 --> 00:32:54.628
Be careful. Third Sister.

316
00:32:54.711 --> 00:32:56.461
You go too far.

317
00:32:58.336 --> 00:33:00.086
Maybe you don't go far enough.

318
00:33:11.128 --> 00:33:12.170
Thank you. Owen.

319
00:33:18.461 --> 00:33:19.920
I didn't do it for you.

320
00:33:57.211 --> 00:33:59.045
Right on time as always.

321
00:33:59.128 --> 00:34:00.461
Anything good today?

322
00:34:00.545 --> 00:34:03.003
A trade ship and an Aquillian Ranger.

323
00:34:03.086 --> 00:34:04.836
Probably scouring for pirates.

324
00:34:04.920 --> 00:34:06.461
That's what I said.

325
00:34:06.545 --> 00:34:08.420
- Don't encourage her.
- All right.

326
00:34:11.711 --> 00:34:12.920
Come now.

327
00:34:13.003 --> 00:34:14.628
Let's get this over with.

328
00:34:19.920 --> 00:34:21.086
- Breha.
- Sister.

329
00:34:21.170 --> 00:34:22.420
- Greetings.
- Hi. cousin.

330
00:34:27.378 --> 00:34:28.420
Princess.

331
00:34:28.503 --> 00:34:30.836
Oh. there they are.

332
00:34:30.920 --> 00:34:32.086
Princess.

333
00:34:33.128 --> 00:34:34.461
Hi. Princess.

334
00:34:46.753 --> 00:34:48.086
Profits have been good.

335
00:34:48.961 --> 00:34:54.003
After the disaster of the Republic.
the Empire is finally lining some pockets.

336
00:34:54.086 --> 00:34:56.795
There are still some issues
that we need to address.

337
00:34:57.378 --> 00:34:59.836
Slave labor. taxation of the Outer Rim...

338
00:34:59.920 --> 00:35:02.420
I didn't come here to end slavery. Bail.

339
00:35:03.086 --> 00:35:04.795
I came to eat your food.

340
00:35:05.586 --> 00:35:07.253
Save the bleeding heart for the Senate.

341
00:35:07.961 --> 00:35:09.878
A drink. Senator?

342
00:35:11.461 --> 00:35:13.170
Ah. Thank you.

343
00:35:17.045 --> 00:35:18.128
Your Highness.

344
00:35:18.420 --> 00:35:19.836
Oh. Thanks. Y-O.

345
00:35:19.920 --> 00:35:21.003
My pleasure.

346
00:35:22.170 --> 00:35:23.378
You thank your droids?

347
00:35:24.003 --> 00:35:25.503
It's good manners.

348
00:35:25.586 --> 00:35:28.503
You don't need manners
when you're talking to a lower life form.

349
00:35:28.586 --> 00:35:31.753
Then I guess I don't need manners
when I'm talking to you.

350
00:35:34.045 --> 00:35:36.628
You know the difference
between you and me. cousin?

351
00:35:37.336 --> 00:35:38.336
I know things.

352
00:35:38.920 --> 00:35:41.503
My father says
they never let you leave this planet.

353
00:35:42.711 --> 00:35:46.295
They don't want anybody to know about you
because you're not one of us.

354
00:35:47.336 --> 00:35:48.836
You're not even a real Organa.

355
00:35:53.545 --> 00:35:54.961
You're scared of him.

356
00:35:56.170 --> 00:35:59.711
Your father. You want him to like you.
so you repeat what he says

357
00:35:59.795 --> 00:36:02.211
even though you don't really know
what it means.

358
00:36:03.086 --> 00:36:05.878
You think being like him
will make people frightened of you.

359
00:36:05.961 --> 00:36:08.628
but really. you're the one who's scared.

360
00:36:08.711 --> 00:36:11.461
You've never made one decision
for yourself in your entire life.

361
00:36:11.545 --> 00:36:13.253
and you never will.

362
00:36:14.086 --> 00:36:16.878
I may not have seen much. cousin.

363
00:36:18.045 --> 00:36:19.295
but I can see that.

364
00:36:25.795 --> 00:36:27.711
He was being horrible to everyone.

365
00:36:27.795 --> 00:36:28.920
He's your cousin.

366
00:36:29.003 --> 00:36:30.503
He's rude to droids.

367
00:36:30.586 --> 00:36:32.836
You have to rise above. Leia.

368
00:36:35.586 --> 00:36:36.920
You owe him an apology.

369
00:36:37.378 --> 00:36:40.336
I'd rather be digested by a jakobeast.

370
00:36:52.170 --> 00:36:56.586
I wanted to live out way past Kathou
when I was your age.

371
00:36:57.545 --> 00:37:00.378
Chase purrgil. you know?

372
00:37:00.461 --> 00:37:01.961
I had a whole plan.

373
00:37:03.753 --> 00:37:04.753
What happened?

374
00:37:05.503 --> 00:37:06.586
I got older.

375
00:37:07.461 --> 00:37:09.503
Had to find some other adventures.

376
00:37:10.503 --> 00:37:12.253
Started chasing your mother instead.

377
00:37:15.045 --> 00:37:16.711
This is your future. Leia.

378
00:37:17.503 --> 00:37:20.503
In a few years. you'll be
off to university. then Junior Senate.

379
00:37:20.586 --> 00:37:21.586
The Senate's boring.

380
00:37:21.670 --> 00:37:24.086
It's people in itchy clothes arguing.

381
00:37:24.170 --> 00:37:27.086
Well. it may seem so...

382
00:37:27.170 --> 00:37:28.420
I don't want to be a senator.

383
00:37:28.961 --> 00:37:31.628
It is why
you'll probably be one of the best.

384
00:37:32.836 --> 00:37:34.795
I'm not even a real Organa.

385
00:37:35.711 --> 00:37:36.711
What?

386
00:37:41.461 --> 00:37:42.461
Don't ever say that.

387
00:37:44.586 --> 00:37:45.753
You are our child.

388
00:37:47.170 --> 00:37:51.295
You are an Organa in every way.

389
00:37:53.420 --> 00:37:55.711
One day. this planet
will look to you. Leia.

390
00:37:57.961 --> 00:37:59.461
There are many ways to lead.

391
00:37:59.545 --> 00:38:01.795
You just have to find yours.

392
00:38:01.878 --> 00:38:04.545
Plus. imagine the look
on your cousin's face

393
00:38:04.628 --> 00:38:06.711
when you get to boss him around for real.

394
00:38:10.753 --> 00:38:11.836
But for now.

395
00:38:13.711 --> 00:38:14.795
we will...

396
00:38:16.586 --> 00:38:17.753
apologize.

397
00:38:18.711 --> 00:38:19.711
Yes. Father.

398
00:38:19.795 --> 00:38:20.795
Hmm.

399
00:38:25.711 --> 00:38:27.211
I'll wait for you downstairs.

400
00:38:43.628 --> 00:38:44.711
Thank you.

401
00:38:45.295 --> 00:38:46.378
She's gone.

402
00:38:46.586 --> 00:38:48.795
I thought you said
you've really got through to her.

403
00:38:49.295 --> 00:38:50.461
You know what she's like.

404
00:38:50.545 --> 00:38:51.961
I know who she's like.

405
00:38:52.711 --> 00:38:53.878
Send a unit.

406
00:38:53.961 --> 00:38:54.961
She can't be far.

407
00:39:02.378 --> 00:39:04.003
Hello. Princess.

408
00:39:06.211 --> 00:39:07.378
Why are you here?

409
00:39:08.420 --> 00:39:09.503
Just waiting.

410
00:39:09.961 --> 00:39:11.295
For what?

411
00:39:11.961 --> 00:39:13.295
For you.

412
00:39:54.253 --> 00:39:55.336
Help!

413
00:39:56.795 --> 00:39:57.878
Help!

414
00:39:59.295 --> 00:40:00.878
Help! Help me. please!

415
00:40:40.336 --> 00:40:41.920
<i>We don't know who it was.</i>

416
00:40:42.003 --> 00:40:43.628
<i>No ransom. no leads.</i>

417
00:40:44.961 --> 00:40:49.086
<i>Whoever they are.
they knew where she would be. They...</i>

418
00:40:49.795 --> 00:40:50.878
<i>They were waiting.</i>

419
00:40:52.253 --> 00:40:54.170
<i>She needs you. Obi-Wan.</i>

420
00:40:55.211 --> 00:40:56.711
<i>We can't trust anyone else.</i>

421
00:40:58.878 --> 00:41:00.295
What about the Senate?

422
00:41:00.795 --> 00:41:02.545
<i>We cannot let this become public.</i>

423
00:41:03.211 --> 00:41:04.961
<i>It would draw too much attention.</i>

424
00:41:05.795 --> 00:41:08.711
Well. your guard then? Or a bounty hunter?

425
00:41:08.795 --> 00:41:12.878
<i>Only you know how important
she really is. Obi-Wan.</i>

426
00:41:12.961 --> 00:41:14.545
<i>If Leia is discovered...</i>

427
00:41:14.628 --> 00:41:16.211
I can't leave here. Bail.

428
00:41:17.420 --> 00:41:18.586
My duty is to the boy...

429
00:41:18.670 --> 00:41:20.586
<i>What about your duty to his sister?</i>

430
00:41:22.420 --> 00:41:24.253
<i>She's as important as he is.</i>

431
00:41:30.461 --> 00:41:31.961
It's been ten years.

432
00:41:35.670 --> 00:41:37.086
I'm not who I used to be.

433
00:41:43.211 --> 00:41:44.295
Find someone else.

434
00:41:45.920 --> 00:41:47.086
She'll be better off.

435
00:41:50.836 --> 00:41:53.295
Let go of me!

436
00:41:53.378 --> 00:41:54.836
- Let go!
- Shut her up.

437
00:43:40.295 --> 00:43:41.878
She's headed for Daiyu.

438
00:43:44.045 --> 00:43:45.795
You should not have come.

439
00:43:46.753 --> 00:43:49.128
They hid their signature
behind a freight transport.

440
00:43:49.211 --> 00:43:51.045
The ship is on its way there now.

441
00:43:51.795 --> 00:43:52.836
I can't.

442
00:43:52.920 --> 00:43:54.670
She's my daughter. Obi-Wan.

443
00:43:54.753 --> 00:43:55.920
I told you...

444
00:43:57.003 --> 00:43:58.461
I'm not the man you remember.

445
00:43:58.545 --> 00:43:59.878
You're going to have to be!

446
00:43:59.961 --> 00:44:01.086
I can't leave the boy.

447
00:44:01.170 --> 00:44:03.086
This isn't about the boy. and you know it!

448
00:44:04.211 --> 00:44:06.170
You've made mistakes. We all did.

449
00:44:06.253 --> 00:44:07.503
It's the past.

450
00:44:08.461 --> 00:44:09.961
Move on. Be done with it.

451
00:44:11.003 --> 00:44:12.670
You couldn't save Anakin.

452
00:44:14.628 --> 00:44:15.961
but you can save her.

453
00:44:18.586 --> 00:44:19.836
And what if I can't?

454
00:44:22.211 --> 00:44:25.128
There is no one
I trust more with my child than you.

455
00:44:27.003 --> 00:44:29.711
Please. old friend.

456
00:44:31.461 --> 00:44:32.545
For her.

457
00:44:33.920 --> 00:44:35.170
One last fight.

458
00:44:44.878 --> 00:44:47.961
Come on. Lola. Come on.

459
00:45:01.670 --> 00:45:03.170
Can you untie me?

460
00:45:11.503 --> 00:45:13.211
I'm not afraid of you.

461
00:45:15.295 --> 00:45:16.461
Give it time.

462
00:45:22.336 --> 00:45:23.461
Lola!

463
00:45:24.836 --> 00:45:27.128
My father will rescue me!

464
00:45:27.211 --> 00:45:29.170
He'll send a whole army!

465
00:45:29.753 --> 00:45:31.586
No one's coming for you.

466
00:46:28.670 --> 00:46:29.920
This is a bad idea.

467
00:46:30.670 --> 00:46:31.753
Kidnapping kids...

468
00:46:33.378 --> 00:46:34.545
you think it's gonna work?

469
00:46:35.128 --> 00:46:36.545
Just get this over with.

470
00:47:17.378 --> 00:47:18.711
You sure he's gonna come?

471
00:47:19.586 --> 00:47:21.753
<i>He fought beside her father
during the war.</i>

472
00:47:22.711 --> 00:47:23.795
<i>He'll come.</i>

473
00:47:24.795 --> 00:47:26.295
<i>He won't be able to help it.</i>

474
00:47:27.503 --> 00:47:29.753
<i>The Jedi will hunt himself.</i>

475
00:47:56.961 --> 00:47:58.420
Well?

476
00:47:58.503 --> 00:47:59.670
You coming or not?
